            <title>[HIVE-197] UDFToBoolean flipping values</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-197</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;UDFToBoolean should do&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;return Boolean.valueOf(i.byteValue() != 0)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead of&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;return Boolean.valueOf(i.byteValue() == 0)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Same for all other types.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
