                            <comment id="12659060" author="rsm" created="Wed, 24 Dec 2008 08:17:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;looks good.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Btw do we want to support casting any random string to boolean? Mysql seems to just convert the string to an integer and return false only if the integer is 0, else true.&lt;br/&gt;
But its not consistent.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example: SELECT IF(&quot;10&quot;, TRUE, FALSE) returns 1 but SELECT &quot;10&quot; = TRUE; returns 0.&lt;/p&gt;

